2530/* If TT is a variable or function decl replace it with its
2531 prevailing variant. */
2532#define LTO_SET_PREVAIL(tt) \
2533 do {\
2534 if ((tt) && VAR_OR_FUNCTION_DECL_P (tt) \
2535 && (TREE_PUBLIC (tt) || DECL_EXTERNAL (tt))) \
2536 { \
2537 tt = lto_symtab_prevailing_decl (tt); \
2538 fixed = true; \
2539 } \
2540 } while (0)
2541
2542/* Ensure that TT isn't a replacable var of function decl. */
2543#define LTO_NO_PREVAIL(tt) \
2544 gcc_checking_assert (!(tt) || !VAR_OR_FUNCTION_DECL_P (tt))
2545
2546/* Given a tree T replace all fields referring to variables or functions
2547 with their prevailing variant. */
2548static void
2549lto_fixup_prevailing_decls (tree t)
2550{
2551 enum tree_code code = TREE_CODE (t);
2552 bool fixed = false;
2553
2554 gcc_checking_assert (code != TREE_BINFO);
2555 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TREE_TYPE (t));
2556 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_COMMON)
2557 /* lto_symtab_prevail_decl use TREE_CHAIN to link to the prevailing decl.
2558 in the case T is a prevailed declaration we would ICE here. */
2559 && !VAR_OR_FUNCTION_DECL_P (t))
2560 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TREE_CHAIN (t));
2561 if (DECL_P (t))
2562 {
2563 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_NAME (t));
2564 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (DECL_CONTEXT (t));
2565 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_COMMON))
2566 {
2567 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (DECL_SIZE (t));
2568 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (DECL_SIZE_UNIT (t));
2569 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (DECL_INITIAL (t));
2570 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_ATTRIBUTES (t));
2571 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (DECL_ABSTRACT_ORIGIN (t));
2572 }
2573 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_WITH_VIS))
2574 {
2575 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (t->decl_with_vis.assembler_name);
2576 }
2577 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_NON_COMMON))
2578 {
2579 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_RESULT_FLD (t));
2580 }
2581 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_FUNCTION_DECL))
2582 {
2583 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_ARGUMENTS (t));
2584 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (DECL_FUNCTION_PERSONALITY (t));
2585 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_VINDEX (t));
2586 }
2587 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_FIELD_DECL))
2588 {
2589 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (DECL_FIELD_OFFSET (t));
2590 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_BIT_FIELD_TYPE (t));
2591 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_QUALIFIER (t));
2592 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_FIELD_BIT_OFFSET (t));
2593 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (DECL_FCONTEXT (t));
2594 }
2595 }
2596 else if (TYPE_P (t))
2597 {
2598 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TYPE_CACHED_VALUES (t));
2599 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TYPE_SIZE (t));
2600 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TYPE_SIZE_UNIT (t));
2601 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TYPE_ATTRIBUTES (t));
2602 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TYPE_NAME (t));
2603
2604 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TYPE_MINVAL (t));
2605 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TYPE_MAXVAL (t));
2606 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (t->type_non_common.binfo);
2607
2608 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TYPE_CONTEXT (t));
2609
2610 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TYPE_CANONICAL (t));
2611 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TYPE_MAIN_VARIANT (t));
2612 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TYPE_NEXT_VARIANT (t));
2613 }
2614 else if (EXPR_P (t))
2615 {
2616 int i;
2617 for (i = TREE_OPERAND_LENGTH (t) - 1; i >= 0; --i)
2618 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TREE_OPERAND (t, i));
2619 }
2620 else if (TREE_CODE (t) == CONSTRUCTOR)
2621 {
2622 unsigned i;
2623 tree val;
2624 FOR_EACH_CONSTRUCTOR_VALUE (CONSTRUCTOR_ELTS (t), i, val)
2625 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (val);
2626 }
2627 else
2628 {
2629 switch (code)
2630 {
2631 case TREE_LIST:
2632 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TREE_VALUE (t));
2633 LTO_SET_PREVAIL (TREE_PURPOSE (t));
2634 LTO_NO_PREVAIL (TREE_PURPOSE (t));
2635 break;
2636 default:
2637 gcc_unreachable ();
2638 }
2639 }
2640 /* If we fixed nothing, then we missed something seen by
2641 mentions_vars_p. */
2642 gcc_checking_assert (fixed);
2643}
2644#undef LTO_SET_PREVAIL
2645#undef LTO_NO_PREVAIL
2646
2647/* Helper function of lto_fixup_decls. Walks the var and fn streams in STATE,
2648 replaces var and function decls with the corresponding prevailing def. */
2649
2650static void
2651lto_fixup_state (struct lto_in_decl_state *state)
2652{
2653 unsigned i, si;
2654
2655 /* Although we only want to replace FUNCTION_DECLs and VAR_DECLs,
2656 we still need to walk from all DECLs to find the reachable
2657 FUNCTION_DECLs and VAR_DECLs. */
2658 for (si = 0; si < LTO_N_DECL_STREAMS; si++)
2659 {
2660 vec<tree, va_gc> *trees = state->streams[si];
2661 for (i = 0; i < vec_safe_length (trees); i++)
2662 {
2663 tree t = (*trees)[i];
2664 if (flag_checking && TYPE_P (t))
2665 verify_type (t);
2666 if (VAR_OR_FUNCTION_DECL_P (t)
2667 && (TREE_PUBLIC (t) || DECL_EXTERNAL (t)))
2668 (*trees)[i] = lto_symtab_prevailing_decl (t);
2669 }
2670 }
2671}
2672
2673/* Fix the decls from all FILES. Replaces each decl with the corresponding
2674 prevailing one. */
2675
2676static void
2677lto_fixup_decls (struct lto_file_decl_data **files)
2678{
2679 unsigned int i;
2680 tree t;
2681
2682 if (tree_with_vars)
2683 FOR_EACH_VEC_ELT ((*tree_with_vars), i, t)
2684 lto_fixup_prevailing_decls (t);
2685
2686 for (i = 0; files[i]; i++)
2687 {
2688 struct lto_file_decl_data *file = files[i];
2689 struct lto_in_decl_state *state = file->global_decl_state;
2690 lto_fixup_state (state);
2691
2692 hash_table<decl_state_hasher>::iterator iter;
2693 lto_in_decl_state *elt;
2694 FOR_EACH_HASH_TABLE_ELEMENT (*file->function_decl_states, elt,
2695 lto_in_decl_state *, iter)
2696 lto_fixup_state (elt);
2697 }
2698}

2700static GTY((length ("lto_stats.num_input_files + 1"))) struct lto_file_decl_data **all_file_decl_data;
2701
2702/* Turn file datas for sub files into a single array, so that they look
2703 like separate files for further passes. */
2704
2705static void
2706lto_flatten_files (struct lto_file_decl_data **orig, int count, int last_file_ix)
2707{
2708 struct lto_file_decl_data *n, *next;
2709 int i, k;
2710
2711 lto_stats.num_input_files = count;
2712 all_file_decl_data
2713 = ggc_cleared_vec_alloc<lto_file_decl_data_ptr> (count + 1);
2714 /* Set the hooks so that all of the ipa passes can read in their data. */
2715 lto_set_in_hooks (all_file_decl_data, get_section_data, free_section_data);
2716 for (i = 0, k = 0; i < last_file_ix; i++)
2717 {
2718 for (n = orig[i]; n != NULL; n = next)
2719 {
2720 all_file_decl_data[k++] = n;
2721 next = n->next;
2722 n->next = NULL;
2723 }
2724 }
2725 all_file_decl_data[k] = NULL;
2726 gcc_assert (k == count);
2727}
2728
2729/* Input file data before flattening (i.e. splitting them to subfiles to support
2730 incremental linking. */
2731static int real_file_count;
2732static GTY((length ("real_file_count + 1"))) struct lto_file_decl_data **real_file_decl_data;
2733
2734static void print_lto_report_1 (void);
2735
2736/* Read all the symbols from the input files FNAMES. NFILES is the
2737 number of files requested in the command line. Instantiate a
2738 global call graph by aggregating all the sub-graphs found in each
2739 file. */
2740
2741static void
2742read_cgraph_and_symbols (unsigned nfiles, const char **fnames)
2743{
2744 unsigned int i, last_file_ix;
2745 FILE *resolution;
2746 int count = 0;
2747 struct lto_file_decl_data **decl_data;
2748 symtab_node *snode;
2749
2750 symtab->initialize ();
2751
2752 timevar_push (TV_IPA_LTO_DECL_IN);
2753
2754#ifdef ACCEL_COMPILER
2755 section_name_prefix = OFFLOAD_SECTION_NAME_PREFIX;
2756 lto_stream_offload_p = true;
2757#endif
2758
2759 real_file_decl_data
2760 = decl_data = ggc_cleared_vec_alloc<lto_file_decl_data_ptr> (nfiles + 1);
2761 real_file_count = nfiles;
2762
2763 /* Read the resolution file. */
2764 resolution = NULL;
2765 if (resolution_file_name)
2766 {
2767 int t;
2768 unsigned num_objects;
2769
2770 resolution = fopen (resolution_file_name, "r");
2771 if (resolution == NULL)
2772 fatal_error (input_location,
2773 "could not open symbol resolution file: %m");
2774
2775 t = fscanf (resolution, "%u", &num_objects);
2776 gcc_assert (t == 1);
2777
2778 /* True, since the plugin splits the archives. */
2779 gcc_assert (num_objects == nfiles);
2780 }
2781 symtab->state = LTO_STREAMING;
2782
2783 canonical_type_hash_cache = new hash_map<const_tree, hashval_t> (251);
2784 gimple_canonical_types = htab_create (16381, gimple_canonical_type_hash,
2785 gimple_canonical_type_eq, NULL);
2786 gcc_obstack_init (&tree_scc_hash_obstack);
2787 tree_scc_hash = new hash_table<tree_scc_hasher> (4096);
2788
2789 /* Register the common node types with the canonical type machinery so
2790 we properly share alias-sets across languages and TUs. Do not
2791 expose the common nodes as type merge target - those that should be
2792 are already exposed so by pre-loading the LTO streamer caches.
2793 Do two passes - first clear TYPE_CANONICAL and then re-compute it. */
2794 for (i = 0; i < itk_none; ++i)
2795 lto_register_canonical_types (integer_types[i], true);
2796 for (i = 0; i < stk_type_kind_last; ++i)
2797 lto_register_canonical_types (sizetype_tab[i], true);
2798 for (i = 0; i < TI_MAX; ++i)
2799 lto_register_canonical_types (global_trees[i], true);
2800 for (i = 0; i < itk_none; ++i)
2801 lto_register_canonical_types (integer_types[i], false);
2802 for (i = 0; i < stk_type_kind_last; ++i)
2803 lto_register_canonical_types (sizetype_tab[i], false);
2804 for (i = 0; i < TI_MAX; ++i)
2805 lto_register_canonical_types (global_trees[i], false);
2806
2807 if (!quiet_flag)
2808 fprintf (stderr, "Reading object files:");
2809
2810 /* Read all of the object files specified on the command line. */
2811 for (i = 0, last_file_ix = 0; i < nfiles; ++i)
2812 {
2813 struct lto_file_decl_data *file_data = NULL;
2814 if (!quiet_flag)
2815 {
2816 fprintf (stderr, " %s", fnames[i]);
2817 fflush (stderr);
2818 }
2819
2820 current_lto_file = lto_obj_file_open (fnames[i], false);
2821 if (!current_lto_file)
2822 break;
2823
2824 file_data = lto_file_read (current_lto_file, resolution, &count);
2825 if (!file_data)
2826 {
2827 lto_obj_file_close (current_lto_file);
2828 free (current_lto_file);
2829 current_lto_file = NULL;
2830 break;
2831 }
2832
2833 decl_data[last_file_ix++] = file_data;
2834
2835 lto_obj_file_close (current_lto_file);
2836 free (current_lto_file);
2837 current_lto_file = NULL;
2838 }
2839
2840 lto_flatten_files (decl_data, count, last_file_ix);
2841 lto_stats.num_input_files = count;
2842 ggc_free(decl_data);
2843 real_file_decl_data = NULL;
2844
2845 if (resolution_file_name)
2846 fclose (resolution);
2847
2848 /* Show the LTO report before launching LTRANS. */
2849 if (flag_lto_report || (flag_wpa && flag_lto_report_wpa))
2850 print_lto_report_1 ();
2851
2852 /* Free gimple type merging datastructures. */
2853 delete tree_scc_hash;
2854 tree_scc_hash = NULL;
2855 obstack_free (&tree_scc_hash_obstack, NULL);
2856 htab_delete (gimple_canonical_types);
2857 gimple_canonical_types = NULL;
2858 delete canonical_type_hash_cache;
2859 canonical_type_hash_cache = NULL;
2860
2861 /* At this stage we know that majority of GGC memory is reachable.
2862 Growing the limits prevents unnecesary invocation of GGC. */
2863 ggc_grow ();
2864 ggc_collect ();
2865
2866 /* Set the hooks so that all of the ipa passes can read in their data. */
2867 lto_set_in_hooks (all_file_decl_data, get_section_data, free_section_data);
2868
2869 timevar_pop (TV_IPA_LTO_DECL_IN);
2870
2871 if (!quiet_flag)
2872 fprintf (stderr, "\nReading the callgraph\n");
2873
2874 timevar_push (TV_IPA_LTO_CGRAPH_IO);
2875 /* Read the symtab. */
2876 input_symtab ();
2877
2878 input_offload_tables (!flag_ltrans);
2879
2880 /* Store resolutions into the symbol table. */
2881
2882 FOR_EACH_SYMBOL (snode)
2883 if (snode->externally_visible && snode->real_symbol_p ()
2884 && snode->lto_file_data && snode->lto_file_data->resolution_map
2885 && !is_builtin_fn (snode->decl)
2886 && !(VAR_P (snode->decl) && DECL_HARD_REGISTER (snode->decl)))
2887 {
2888 ld_plugin_symbol_resolution_t *res;
2889
2890 res = snode->lto_file_data->resolution_map->get (snode->decl);
2891 if (!res || *res == LDPR_UNKNOWN)
2892 {
2893 if (snode->output_to_lto_symbol_table_p ())
2894 fatal_error (input_location, "missing resolution data for %s",
2895 IDENTIFIER_POINTER
2896 (DECL_ASSEMBLER_NAME (snode->decl)));
2897 }
2898 else
2899 snode->resolution = *res;
2900 }
2901 for (i = 0; all_file_decl_data[i]; i++)
2902 if (all_file_decl_data[i]->resolution_map)
2903 {
2904 delete all_file_decl_data[i]->resolution_map;
2905 all_file_decl_data[i]->resolution_map = NULL;
2906 }
2907
2908 timevar_pop (TV_IPA_LTO_CGRAPH_IO);
2909
2910 if (!quiet_flag)
2911 fprintf (stderr, "Merging declarations\n");
2912
2913 timevar_push (TV_IPA_LTO_DECL_MERGE);
2914 /* Merge global decls. In ltrans mode we read merged cgraph, we do not
2915 need to care about resolving symbols again, we only need to replace
2916 duplicated declarations read from the callgraph and from function
2917 sections. */
2918 if (!flag_ltrans)
2919 {
2920 lto_symtab_merge_decls ();
2921
2922 /* If there were errors during symbol merging bail out, we have no
2923 good way to recover here. */
2924 if (seen_error ())
2925 fatal_error (input_location,
2926 "errors during merging of translation units");
2927
2928 /* Fixup all decls. */
2929 lto_fixup_decls (all_file_decl_data);
2930 }
2931 if (tree_with_vars)
2932 ggc_free (tree_with_vars);
2933 tree_with_vars = NULL;
2934 ggc_collect ();
2935
2936 timevar_pop (TV_IPA_LTO_DECL_MERGE);
2937 /* Each pass will set the appropriate timer. */
2938
2939 if (!quiet_flag)
2940 fprintf (stderr, "Reading summaries\n");
2941
2942 /* Read the IPA summary data. */
2943 if (flag_ltrans)
2944 ipa_read_optimization_summaries ();
2945 else
2946 ipa_read_summaries ();
2947
2948 for (i = 0; all_file_decl_data[i]; i++)
2949 {
2950 gcc_assert (all_file_decl_data[i]->symtab_node_encoder);
2951 lto_symtab_encoder_delete (all_file_decl_data[i]->symtab_node_encoder);
2952 all_file_decl_data[i]->symtab_node_encoder = NULL;
2953 lto_free_function_in_decl_state (all_file_decl_data[i]->global_decl_state);
2954 all_file_decl_data[i]->global_decl_state = NULL;
2955 all_file_decl_data[i]->current_decl_state = NULL;
2956 }
2957
2958 /* Finally merge the cgraph according to the decl merging decisions. */
2959 timevar_push (TV_IPA_LTO_CGRAPH_MERGE);
2960 if (symtab->dump_file)
2961 {
2962 fprintf (symtab->dump_file, "Before merging:\n");
2963 symtab_node::dump_table (symtab->dump_file);
2964 }
2965 if (!flag_ltrans)
2966 {
2967 lto_symtab_merge_symbols ();
2968 /* Removal of unreachable symbols is needed to make verify_symtab to pass;
2969 we are still having duplicated comdat groups containing local statics.
2970 We could also just remove them while merging. */
2971 symtab->remove_unreachable_nodes (dump_file);
2972 }
2973 ggc_collect ();
2974 symtab->state = IPA_SSA;
2975 /* FIXME: Technically all node removals happening here are useless, because
2976 WPA should not stream them. */
2977 if (flag_ltrans)
2978 symtab->remove_unreachable_nodes (dump_file);
2979
2980 timevar_pop (TV_IPA_LTO_CGRAPH_MERGE);
2981
2982 /* Indicate that the cgraph is built and ready. */
2983 symtab->function_flags_ready = true;
2984
2985 ggc_free (all_file_decl_data);
2986 all_file_decl_data = NULL;
2987}

2990/* Materialize all the bodies for all the nodes in the callgraph. */
2991
2992static void
2993materialize_cgraph (void)
2994{
2995 struct cgraph_node *node;
2996 timevar_id_t lto_timer;
2997
2998 if (!quiet_flag)
2999 fprintf (stderr,
3000 flag_wpa ? "Materializing decls:" : "Reading function bodies:");
3001
3002
3003 FOR_EACH_FUNCTION (node)
3004 {
3005 if (node->lto_file_data)
3006 {
3007 lto_materialize_function (node);
3008 lto_stats.num_input_cgraph_nodes++;
3009 }
3010 }
3011
3012
3013 /* Start the appropriate timer depending on the mode that we are
3014 operating in. */
3015 lto_timer = (flag_wpa) ? TV_WHOPR_WPA
3016 : (flag_ltrans) ? TV_WHOPR_LTRANS
3017 : TV_LTO;
3018 timevar_push (lto_timer);
3019
3020 current_function_decl = NULL;
3021 set_cfun (NULL);
3022
3023 if (!quiet_flag)
3024 fprintf (stderr, "\n");
3025
3026 timevar_pop (lto_timer);
3027}

3035 fprintf (stderr, "%s statistics\n", pfx);

3073 fprintf (stderr, "[%s] GIMPLE canonical type table: size %ld, "
3074 "%ld elements, %ld searches, %ld collisions (ratio: %f)\n", pfx,
3075 (long) htab_size (gimple_canonical_types),
3076 (long) htab_elements (gimple_canonical_types),
3077 (long) gimple_canonical_types->searches,
3078 (long) gimple_canonical_types->collisions,
3079 htab_collisions (gimple_canonical_types));
3080 fprintf (stderr, "[%s] GIMPLE canonical type pointer-map: "
3081 "%lu elements, %ld searches\n", pfx,
3082 num_canonical_type_hash_entries,
3083 num_canonical_type_hash_queries);
3084 }
3085
3086 print_lto_report (pfx);
3087}
3088
3089/* Perform whole program analysis (WPA) on the callgraph and write out the
3090 optimization plan. */
3091
3092static void
3093do_whole_program_analysis (void)
3094{
3095 symtab_node *node;
3096
3097 lto_parallelism = 1;
3098
3099 /* TODO: jobserver communicatoin is not supported, yet. */
3100 if (!strcmp (flag_wpa, "jobserver"))
3101 lto_parallelism = -1;
3102 else
3103 {
3104 lto_parallelism = atoi (flag_wpa);
3105 if (lto_parallelism <= 0)
3106 lto_parallelism = 0;
3107 }
3108
3109 timevar_start (TV_PHASE_OPT_GEN);
3110
3111 /* Note that since we are in WPA mode, materialize_cgraph will not
3112 actually read in all the function bodies. It only materializes
3113 the decls and cgraph nodes so that analysis can be performed. */
3114 materialize_cgraph ();
3115
3116 /* Reading in the cgraph uses different timers, start timing WPA now. */
3117 timevar_push (TV_WHOPR_WPA);
3118
3119 if (pre_ipa_mem_report)
3120 {
3121 fprintf (stderr, "Memory consumption before IPA\n");
3122 dump_memory_report (false);
3123 }
3124
3125 symtab->function_flags_ready = true;
3126
3127 if (symtab->dump_file)
3128 symtab_node::dump_table (symtab->dump_file);
3129 bitmap_obstack_initialize (NULL);
3130 symtab->state = IPA_SSA;
3131
3132 execute_ipa_pass_list (g->get_passes ()->all_regular_ipa_passes);
3133
3134 /* When WPA analysis raises errors, do not bother to output anything. */
3135 if (seen_error ())
3136 return;
3137
3138 if (symtab->dump_file)
3139 {
3140 fprintf (symtab->dump_file, "Optimized ");
3141 symtab_node::dump_table (symtab->dump_file);
3142 }
3143
3144 symtab_node::checking_verify_symtab_nodes ();
3145 bitmap_obstack_release (NULL);
3146
3147 /* We are about to launch the final LTRANS phase, stop the WPA timer. */
3148 timevar_pop (TV_WHOPR_WPA);
3149
3150 timevar_push (TV_WHOPR_PARTITIONING);
3151 if (flag_lto_partition == LTO_PARTITION_1TO1)
3152 lto_1_to_1_map ();
3153 else if (flag_lto_partition == LTO_PARTITION_MAX)
3154 lto_max_map ();
3155 else if (flag_lto_partition == LTO_PARTITION_ONE)
3156 lto_balanced_map (1, INT_MAX);
3157 else if (flag_lto_partition == LTO_PARTITION_BALANCED)
3158 lto_balanced_map (PARAM_VALUE (PARAM_LTO_PARTITIONS),
3159 PARAM_VALUE (MAX_PARTITION_SIZE));
3160 else
3161 gcc_unreachable ();
3162
3163 /* Inline summaries are needed for balanced partitioning. Free them now so
3164 the memory can be used for streamer caches. */
3165 inline_free_summary ();
3166
3167 /* AUX pointers are used by partitioning code to bookkeep number of
3168 partitions symbol is in. This is no longer needed. */
3169 FOR_EACH_SYMBOL (node)
3170 node->aux = NULL;
3171
3172 lto_stats.num_cgraph_partitions += ltrans_partitions.length ();
3173
3174 /* Find out statics that need to be promoted
3175 to globals with hidden visibility because they are accessed from multiple
3176 partitions. */
3177 lto_promote_cross_file_statics ();
3178 timevar_pop (TV_WHOPR_PARTITIONING);
3179
3180 timevar_stop (TV_PHASE_OPT_GEN);
3181
3182 /* Collect a last time - in lto_wpa_write_files we may end up forking
3183 with the idea that this doesn't increase memory usage. So we
3184 absoultely do not want to collect after that. */
3185 ggc_collect ();
3186
3187 timevar_start (TV_PHASE_STREAM_OUT);
3188 if (!quiet_flag)
3189 {
3190 fprintf (stderr, "\nStreaming out");
3191 fflush (stderr);
3192 }
3193 lto_wpa_write_files ();
3194 if (!quiet_flag)
3195 fprintf (stderr, "\n");
3196 timevar_stop (TV_PHASE_STREAM_OUT);
3197
3198 if (post_ipa_mem_report)
3199 {
3200 fprintf (stderr, "Memory consumption after IPA\n");
3201 dump_memory_report (false);
3202 }
3203
3204 /* Show the LTO report before launching LTRANS. */
3205 if (flag_lto_report || (flag_wpa && flag_lto_report_wpa))
3206 print_lto_report_1 ();
3207 if (mem_report_wpa)
3208 dump_memory_report (true);
3209}

3217lto_eh_personality (void)
3218{
3219 if (!lto_eh_personality_decl)
3220 {
3221 /* Use the first personality DECL for our personality if we don't
3222 support multiple ones. This ensures that we don't artificially
3223 create the need for them in a single-language program. */
3224 if (first_personality_decl && !dwarf2out_do_cfi_asm ())
3225 lto_eh_personality_decl = first_personality_decl;
3226 else
3227 lto_eh_personality_decl = lhd_gcc_personality ();

3268/* Create artificial pointers for "omp declare target link" vars. */
3269
3270static void
3271offload_handle_link_vars (void)
3272{
3273#ifdef ACCEL_COMPILER
3274 varpool_node *var;
3275 FOR_EACH_VARIABLE (var)
3276 if (lookup_attribute ("omp declare target link",
3277 DECL_ATTRIBUTES (var->decl)))
3278 {
3279 tree type = build_pointer_type (TREE_TYPE (var->decl));
3280 tree link_ptr_var = make_node (VAR_DECL);
3281 TREE_TYPE (link_ptr_var) = type;
3282 TREE_USED (link_ptr_var) = 1;
3283 TREE_STATIC (link_ptr_var) = 1;
3284 SET_DECL_MODE (link_ptr_var, TYPE_MODE (type));
3285 DECL_SIZE (link_ptr_var) = TYPE_SIZE (type);
3286 DECL_SIZE_UNIT (link_ptr_var) = TYPE_SIZE_UNIT (type);
3287 DECL_ARTIFICIAL (link_ptr_var) = 1;
3288 tree var_name = DECL_ASSEMBLER_NAME (var->decl);
3289 char *new_name
3290 = ACONCAT ((IDENTIFIER_POINTER (var_name), "_linkptr", NULL));
3291 DECL_NAME (link_ptr_var) = get_identifier (new_name);
3292 SET_DECL_ASSEMBLER_NAME (link_ptr_var, DECL_NAME (link_ptr_var));
3293 SET_DECL_VALUE_EXPR (var->decl, build_simple_mem_ref (link_ptr_var));
3294 DECL_HAS_VALUE_EXPR_P (var->decl) = 1;
3295 }
3296#endif
3297}

3300/* Main entry point for the GIMPLE front end. This front end has
3301 three main personalities:
3302
3303 - LTO (-flto). All the object files on the command line are
3304 loaded in memory and processed as a single translation unit.
3305 This is the traditional link-time optimization behavior.
3306
3307 - WPA (-fwpa). Only the callgraph and summary information for
3308 files in the command file are loaded. A single callgraph
3309 (without function bodies) is instantiated for the whole set of
3310 files. IPA passes are only allowed to analyze the call graph
3311 and make transformation decisions. The callgraph is
3312 partitioned, each partition is written to a new object file
3313 together with the transformation decisions.
3314
3315 - LTRANS (-fltrans). Similar to -flto but it prevents the IPA
3316 summary files from running again. Since WPA computed summary
3317 information and decided what transformations to apply, LTRANS
3318 simply applies them. */
3319
3320void
3321lto_main (void)
3322{
3323 /* LTO is called as a front end, even though it is not a front end.
3324 Because it is called as a front end, TV_PHASE_PARSING and
3325 TV_PARSE_GLOBAL are active, and we need to turn them off while
3326 doing LTO. Later we turn them back on so they are active up in
3327 toplev.c. */
3328 timevar_pop (TV_PARSE_GLOBAL);
3329 timevar_stop (TV_PHASE_PARSING);
3330
3331 timevar_start (TV_PHASE_SETUP);
3332
3333 /* Initialize the LTO front end. */
3334 lto_init ();
3335
3336 timevar_stop (TV_PHASE_SETUP);
3337 timevar_start (TV_PHASE_STREAM_IN);
3338
3339 /* Read all the symbols and call graph from all the files in the
3340 command line. */
3341 read_cgraph_and_symbols (num_in_fnames, in_fnames);
3342
3343 timevar_stop (TV_PHASE_STREAM_IN);
3344
3345 if (!seen_error ())
3346 {
3347 offload_handle_link_vars ();
3348
3349 /* If WPA is enabled analyze the whole call graph and create an
3350 optimization plan. Otherwise, read in all the function
3351 bodies and continue with optimization. */
3352 if (flag_wpa)
3353 do_whole_program_analysis ();
3354 else
3355 {
3356 timevar_start (TV_PHASE_OPT_GEN);
3357
3358 materialize_cgraph ();
3359 if (!flag_ltrans)
3360 lto_promote_statics_nonwpa ();
3361
3362 /* Annotate the CU DIE and mark the early debug phase as finished. */
3363 debug_hooks->early_finish ("<artificial>");
3364
3365 /* Let the middle end know that we have read and merged all of
3366 the input files. */
3367 symtab->compile ();
3368
3369 timevar_stop (TV_PHASE_OPT_GEN);
3370
3371 /* FIXME lto, if the processes spawned by WPA fail, we miss
3372 the chance to print WPA's report, so WPA will call
3373 print_lto_report before launching LTRANS. If LTRANS was
3374 launched directly by the driver we would not need to do
3375 this. */
3376 if (flag_lto_report || (flag_wpa && flag_lto_report_wpa))
3377 print_lto_report_1 ();
3378 }
3379 }
3380
3381 /* Here we make LTO pretend to be a parser. */
3382 timevar_start (TV_PHASE_PARSING);
3383 timevar_push (TV_PARSE_GLOBAL);
3384}
